{"tid":958360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鴻海最快明年於印度廠房組裝iPhone   調查：中國製造業活動本月或陷入收縮狀態","createTime":"2018-12-27T17:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T03:55:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"611f22a7dee6dedbca21045e6c0bc9269c6c58b9","tid":958360,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T17:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1435265_1_L_20181227181812.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1435265_1_L_20181227181812.jpg&h=f7b4bdd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外電引述消息人士報道，台灣鴻海最快明年起在印度的工廠組裝高端iPhone，例如售價最高的iPhone X系列，是鴻海首度在印度生產iPhone。有關安排亦有助蘋果在印度的拓展更上一層樓。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，將組裝iPhone的廠房位於印度泰米爾納德邦鎮。報道提到，鴻海將投資250億印度盧比擴建廠房，相當於3.56億美元，預計將創造2.5萬個工作崗位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1435296_1_L_20181227215914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1435296_1_L_20181227215914.jpg&h=f491ccc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外電一項調查指出，市場預期中國本月官方製造業採購經理指數（PMI）將跌穿50，是近兩年半以來首次，反映製造業陷入收縮狀態。<br />\n<br />\n外電訪問了27家分析機構得出的預計中值是49.9。數字跌穿50的盛衰分界線除因為天氣轉冷的季節因素影響外，亦由於需求持續低迷。早前因為中美貿易摩擦出現的「搶出口」消退後，工業生產逐步放緩。<br />\n<br />\n國家統計局服務業調查中心將聯同中國物流與採購聯合會，下周一公布採購經理指數月度報告。"},{"pid":"00fcb395ba994a32de334af7a90a5a9bb7492865","tid":958360,"uid":28451,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T18:15:30.000Z","msg":"今年得返三日，最快唔係下年，唔通下個鐘咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b78bfbeed5259fd420c1128cd9316758f40125","tid":958360,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04aee4723bf462f9a582ab24f6d843591c05f98","tid":958360,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b0ead0df9ccbca77d94e3ae56a19c59dfe0852","tid":958360,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:54:17.000Z","msg":"外交部：豈有此理。姓郭的，你是不是中国人？血濃於水呀"},{"pid":"d8bbb4c2431c933fade510ae751663f66051d18b","tid":958360,"uid":124107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:54:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c623835106b9e015eca0854c41247f9cdc9229e","tid":958360,"uid":150347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:55:52.000Z","msg":"過個肥年<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}